Title: MixDoS
Description: MixDoS is an application who helps you control your computer and helps you collect all your batch applications! This application is easier to use than X3ME!
HomeWiki:
Welcome to MixDoS

This is an application for batch files and other console applications!

Version 1.1

+ Created MixDoS Application (if you run it in CMD it will open new window because it is not a console application, it is a windows application who can run without cmd.exe)

 -Mods (D)

-com.exit.cmd (F)

-com.start.cmd (F)

 -mixcode (F)

-MixDoS.exe (F)

-MPT.bat (F)
